          <strong>Wix added AI features.</strong> Traditional platform with AI capabilities layered on.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Zyro is AI-assisted.</strong> AI writer, heatmap tools, content generation built-in.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Pricing Philosophy</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
