        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Target User</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>Wix targets feature-focused users.</strong> People who want extensive capabilities.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Zyro targets budget beginners.</strong> Users wanting AI help at lower prices.
        </p>
