        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">A consultant needed a simple landing page. Services offered, contact form, that's it. Same content, tested both builders.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Zyro test:</strong> Built in 2 minutes. AI Writer generated all the copy. Looked professional. Cost: $9/month.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Wix test:</strong> Built in 3 minutes. But she saw the app marketplace. "I need booking," she thought. Added booking app ($15/mo). "I need live chat," she thought. Added chat app ($10/mo). "I need analytics upgrade."</p>
          <div class="bg-orange-100 border-l-[4px] border-orange-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-orange-900 font-medium"><strong>6 months later:</strong> Wix site cost $52/month (base $17 + apps). Zyro site cost $9/month. That's $258/year difference for features she barely used.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Here's the killer: Both sites generated the same 12 leads. Same conversion rate. Same revenue. The extra features didn't improve results at all.</p>
          <div class="bg-red-100 border-l-[4px] border-red-500 p-4 my-4">
